{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/python-v9/lab-nth-fibonacci-number/build-an-nth-fibonacci-number-calculator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-nth-fibonacci-number","demoType":null,"title":"Implementiraj kalkulator za N-ti Fibonacci broj","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><strong>Cilj:</strong> Popunite korisničke priče navedene ispod i prođite sve testove da biste završili laboratoriju.</p>\n<p><strong>Priče korisnika:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Treba kreirati funkciju sa imenom <code>fibonacci</code>.</li>\n<li>Treba definisati listu sa imenom <code>sequence</code> unutar funkcije <code>fibonacci</code>, i ona mora biti inicijalizovana vrednostima <code>[0, 1]</code>.</li>\n<li>Funkcija <code>fibonacci</code> mora primiti jedan parametar, neujemni ceo broj <code>n</code>.</li>\n<li>Pozivanje <code>fibonacci(n)</code> mora koristiti metodu dinamičkog programiranja (dynamic programming) za izračunavanje i vraćanje <code>n</code>-og broja iz Fibonacijove sekvence, gde je svaki broj zbir prethodnih dva broja.</li>\n<li>Svaki izračunati Fibonacijov broj mora biti dodan u listu <code>sequence</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"68de7360e1832ea180577a8a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":27,"helpCategory":"Python","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"python-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/python-v9/lab-nth-fibonacci-number/build-an-nth-fibonacci-number-calculator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"mainpy","ext":"py","name":"main","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["main.py"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebao bi da ima funkciju sa imenom <code>fibonacci</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert _Node(_code).has_function(\"fibonacci\")`) })"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja funkcija <code>fibonacci</code> treba da primi jedan parametar.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`\r\nfrom inspect import signature\r\nsig = signature(fibonacci)\r\nassert len(sig.parameters) == 1\r\n`) })"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da imate listu sa imenom <code>sequence</code> unutar funkcije <code>fibonacci</code> koja je pokrenuta za <code>[0, 1]</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert _Node(_code).find_function(\"fibonacci\").has_stmt(\"sequence = [0, 1]\")`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(0)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>0</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(0) == 0`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(1)</code> treba vratiti <code>1</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(1) == 1`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(2)</code> treba da vrati <code>1</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(2) == 1`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(3)</code> treba da vrati <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(3) == 2`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(5)</code> treba da vrati <code>5</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(5) == 5`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(10)</code> treba vratiti <code>55</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(10) == 55`) })"},{"text":"<p><code>fibonacci(15)</code> treba da vrati <code>610</code>.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`assert fibonacci(15) == 610`) })"},{"text":"<p>Nije dozvoljeno koristiti recursion u vašem kodu.</p>","testString":"({ test: () => runPython(`\r\nassert not _Node(_code).find_function(\"fibonacci\").find_body().block_has_call(\"fibonacci\")\r\n`) })"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/python-v9/#lab-nth-fibonacci-number","dashedName":"build-an-nth-fibonacci-number-calculator","certification":"python-v9","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"python-v9","chapter":"python","module":"python-dynamic-programming","block":"lab-nth-fibonacci-number","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/python-v9/review-dynamic-programming/review-dynamic-programming","prevChallengePath":"/learn/python-v9/lecture-understanding-dynamic-programming/what-is-dynamic-programming-and-what-are-some-common-algorithms","id":"68de7360e1832ea180577a8a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":27,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"main","ext":"py","contents":"def fibonacci(n):\r\n    sequence = [0, 1]\r\n    \r\n    if n < 2:\r\n        return sequence[n]\r\n    \r\n    for i in range(2, n + 1):\r\n        sequence.append(sequence[i - 1] + sequence[i - 2])\r\n    \r\n    return sequence[n]","history":["main.py"],"fileKey":"mainpy"}]}},"id":"/learn/python-v9/lab-nth-fibonacci-number/build-an-nth-fibonacci-number-calculator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}